{"tid":1927347,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"用紙皮砌咗個窿⋯","createTime":"2020-03-15T17:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T18:34:30.000Z","uid":125817,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3853aa4fbff14febc20194d90f5cf1b492cc1f2","tid":1927347,"uid":125817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NS7eVub.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNS7eVub.png&h=cb8377aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110401107148601/posts/136825784506133/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110401107148601%2Fposts%2F136825784506133%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvjQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=f7384406\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110401107148601/posts/136825784506133/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n話說我順住個社運開始關注社區問題最後去咗<br />\n參選業主立案法團，詳情在以下連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1895784\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1895784</a><br />\n<br />\n之後跟進關於屋苑個垃圾槽口大小冇跟法例嘅情況。<br />\n法例是2018年「勞工處」定垃圾槽口要350mm x 250mm 先係安全嘅工作環境，而我地兆麟苑業主係「場地提供者」，所以要修改返垃圾槽口大細，去符合返一個安全嘅工作環境俾清潔工工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYtRdkE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKYtRdkE.jpg&h=b5f9ecc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以由於呢一個係勞工問題而唔係一個屋宇處相關嘅樓宇問題，所以政府唔願意提供任何津貼，所以叫我地業主自己處理呢一個工作環境不合規格嘅問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYSVE0U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYSVE0U.jpg&h=f4af7651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係法團拖到今時今日都未整，初頭招咗標打算係原本今日舉行嘅業主周年大會表決修改方案，但因為疫情業主周年大會又取消咗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Va0Q7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Va0Q7Q.jpg&h=35f1e555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁問題黎啦，違例㗎嘛，萬一係修改槽口之前有清潔工有咩受傷保險分分鐘可以唔賠，最後如果被索償就係我哋業主交嘅管理費賠返比人，所以法團就出咗份問卷比啲住戶去到揀用咩方案，但係嗰份問卷又唔清唔楚，而且俾人揀嘅方案其實亦都唔係一啲令人好滿意嘅方案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-aSz0uEmLw3c/XmDKKb3Ht7I/AAAAAAAADk0/uPpUrV3grnscOt6tEeNQ1rcj-syvGZ9igCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/20200305173720221_0002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-aSz0uEmLw3c%2FXmDKKb3Ht7I%2FAAAAAAAADk0%2FuPpUrV3grnscOt6tEeNQ1rcj-syvGZ9igCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F20200305173720221_0002.jpg&h=96564d15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xWp8dH-fyIc/XmDKW5RLYaI/AAAAAAAADk8/gDvsHe8gRZA3BApPSyJWx7n_cEtJpczNQCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/20200305173720221_0004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-xWp8dH-fyIc%2FXmDKW5RLYaI%2FAAAAAAAADk8%2FgDvsHe8gRZA3BApPSyJWx7n_cEtJpczNQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F20200305173720221_0004.jpg&h=0aa84862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ndig3cl6mU8/XmDKdFGmMaI/AAAAAAAADlA/7x5By4ugC8s4TXt4X0h7Rck5kny5rgVggCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/20200305173720221_0005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ndig3cl6mU8%2FXmDKdFGmMaI%2FAAAAAAAADlA%2F7x5By4ugC8s4TXt4X0h7Rck5kny5rgVggCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2F20200305173720221_0005.jpg&h=af66cba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以基於自己屋苑自己救，法團唔講我哋講嘅精神。我哋將我哋理解到呢份問卷嘅資料講返俾啲街坊聽，尤其是比較年長嘅一班。上一個星期講完佢哋都唔係好明白，所以有街坊就提議不如整個模型出嚟啦，所以我就用紙皮切咗個垃圾槽口同埋唔同嘅修改垃圾槽口方案嘅組件出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXeMMG7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXeMMG7.png&h=e6f472b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6cKym7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6cKym7.jpg&h=021fdd7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以就最後用紙皮切左垃圾槽呢個窿出嚟囉⋯⋯</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110401107148601/posts/136825784506133/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110401107148601%2Fposts%2F136825784506133%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvjQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=f7384406\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110401107148601/posts/136825784506133/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝收看<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/siulunpeople/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsiulunpeople%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvjQSOVv8pHkqsyXWJi2kweQ%3D&h=fa6f5255\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/siulunpeople/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，由根做起！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9be44be911d6d48827dd045e8ec6982867b1bceb","tid":1927347,"uid":13856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b424dc574099da6862234055439ebf8b0082b980","tid":1927347,"uid":125817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfdde2546a50c9ad0fe7477e1d81555d420531a","tid":1927347,"uid":13856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d478d7c9636e928a1cdd003803dd5ba67b27f2e2","tid":1927347,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T17:20:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港，由自己屋企開始"},{"pid":"89248c34ec493b4f81e1758750f116257b2e5ec4","tid":1927347,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"咁都冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0093300e335461e7eea7602180201aa8521d0b1","tid":1927347,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:34:30.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}